snippet.title: Jikkyou Powerful Major League 2009 (PS2) - Intro
snippet.description:
The intro cinematic for Jikkyou Powerful Major League 2009 for the PlayStation 2. 

This MLB-set spin-off of the Jikkyou Powerful Pro Yakyuu series was never released in the U.S.
